dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.fibex.fibexcore.coretopology

Interface IClientIdRange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IClientIdRange
extends IEntity
    IClientIdRange: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    With this element it is possible to restrict the Client Identifier of the transaction handle that is generated by the client RTE for inter-Ecu Client/Server communication to an allowed range of numerical values.
